001package org.nasdanika.common;
002
003import java.util.Collection;
004import java.util.IdentityHashMap;
005import java.util.Map;
006
007public class ElementIdentityMapCompoundSupplier<T> extends ElementIdentityMapCompoundExecutionParticipant<Supplier<T>,T> implements Supplier<java.util.function.Function<Supplier<T>,T>>  {
008
009        public ElementIdentityMapCompoundSupplier(String name) {
010                super(name);
011        }
012
013        public ElementIdentityMapCompoundSupplier(String name, Collection<Supplier<T>> suppliers) {
014                super(name);
015                suppliers.forEach(this::put);
016        }
017
018        @Override
019        public java.util.function.Function<Supplier<T>,T> execute(ProgressMonitor progressMonitor) {
020                progressMonitor.setWorkRemaining(size());
021                Map<Supplier<T>,T> result = new IdentityHashMap<>();
022                for (Supplier<T> e: elements) {
023                        result.put(e, e.splitAndExecute(progressMonitor));                      
024                }
025                return result::get; 
026        }       
027
028}
